				<p>I was so happy to see this recipe! It&#8217;s a close cousin of my mom&#8217;s famous Blueberry Thing (&#8220;Thing&#8221; because it&#8217;s not quite a cake, not quite a bread&#8230;). Blueberry Thing (provenance unknown) uses sour cream and is dusted only with sugar. The best part is always the gooey center that never quite bakes all the way through. Now I&#8217;m tempted to have a blueberry bake-off to compare the two!</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
